    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FAST, FREQUENT SERVICE\nEST CORA\nAIRLInE°\nEXPANDING IN THE PACIFIC WEST\nWASHINGTON, OREGON AND IDAHO\nAND NOW CALIFORNIA!\nWEST COAST AIRLINES\nYour new key to the Golden Gate!\nEFFECTIVE JULY 31, 1959",
      "PORT\nANGELES\nABERDEEN O\nHOQUIAM\nASTORIA\n(SEASIDE)\nNEWPORT O\nTOLEDO\nROSEBURG\nWASHINGTON\nSEATTLE\nWENATCHEE\n•\nSPOKANE\nPO COUR \u0026 ALEME\nOLYMPIA O\nEPHRATA\nMOSES LAKE\nYAKIMA\nPULLMAN\n• MOsCOw\nWALLA\nWALLA\nPASCO\nRICHLAND O\nKENNEWICK\nO LEWISTON\nCLARKSTON\nPORTLAND\nVANCOUVER\nPENDLETON O\nLA GRANDE O\nO SALEM\nBAKER O\nO ALBANY\nCORVALLIS\nEUGENE\nOREGON\nONTARIO O\nPAYETTE\nBEND\n•\nREDMOND\nBURNS\nMEDFORD O\nKLAMATH\nFALLS\nO LAKEVIEW\nKALISPELL\nCUT BANK\nSHELBY\nGREAT FALLS\nMONTANA\n• McCALL (SEASONAL)\nIDAHO\nSUN VALLEY\nHAILEY\nKETCHUM\nTWIN FALLS\nCALIFORNIA\n• SACRAMENTO\nOAKLAND\nSAN FRANCISCO\n• IDANO FALLS\nBOISE\n• POCATELLO\nBURLEY\n• LOGAN\n• OGDEN\n• SALT LAKE CITY\nUTAH\nNOTE: Service to Salt Lake City, Logan and Ogden to\nstart September 1, 1959.\nService to Omak, Lakeview,\nBurns,\nSun Valley-Hailey-\nKetchum to be inaugurated\nas soon as facilities are\navailable.\nService to Kalispell, Cut Bank-Shelby, Great Falls tenta-\ntively approved by Civil Aeronautics Board and now\nawaiting final decision."
